AllDB ver. 1.0

Copyright (C) Karol BÄ™dkowski 2009-2010

Very simple application for storing various information organised in 
some categories. Each category has own set of fields.

Main features:
- small, fast
- portable
- store all information in one, sqlite database
- import and export to the CSV files
- quick search by filter items list
- tagging items
- portable - written in Python and wxWidgets

This application is similar to the StuffKeeper (http://www.stuffkeeper.com) but simpler.
If you looking for more advanced application - please take a look on it.


